<h1>JavaScript 数组方法</h1> 

<h2>unshift()</h2>

<p>unshift() 方法将新元素添加到数组的开头,并将后续元素的索引加1。并返回新数组的元素长度。</p>

<button onclick="myFunction()">试一试</button>

<p id="demo"></p>
<p id="demo2"></p>
<p id="demo3"></p>

<script>
var fruits = ["Banana", "Orange", "Apple", "Mango"];
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = fruits;

function myFunction() {
  var x = fruits.unshift("Lemon");
  document.getElementById("demo2").innerHTML = "unshift(str)方法将新元素str添加到数组的开头并返回新数组的长度" + x;
  document.getElementById("demo3").innerHTML = fruits;
}
</script>

